'''''Kasidre Kailasa''''' (Kannada: <U+0C95><U+0CBE><U+0CB8><U+0CBF><U+0CA6><U+0CCD><U+0CB0><U+0CC6> <U+0C95><U+0CC8><U+0CB2><U+0CBE><U+0CB8>) is a [[Kannada films of 1971|1971]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Kannada language|Kannada]] film, directed by K. Janakiram and produced by K Janakiram. The film stars [[Rajkumar (actor)|Rajkumar]], [[Udaykumar]], [[Vanisri]] and [[Pandari Bai]] in lead roles. The film had musical score by [[Chellapilla Satyam]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filmibeat.com/kannada/movies/kaasidre-kailasa.html|title=Kasidre Kailasa|accessdate=2015-01-16|publisher=filmibeat.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://chiloka.com/movie/kaasidre-kailasa-1971|title=Kasidre Kailasa|accessdate=2015-01-16|publisher=chiloka.com}}</ref>

